{"title":"剪绳子","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":128,"tags":[],"operation":{"submit":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/problem/1047#submit_code","submissions":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/submissions?problem_id=1047","statistics":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/problem/1047/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/problem/1047/testdata","discussion":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/discussion/problem/1047"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"A君有一根无限长的木桩，木桩上从左到右有无限个小洞，小洞按顺序从1开始编号。\r\n\r\nA君闲来无事开始给小洞系绳子。对于每个偶数m，他在第$m$个洞到$m/2$个洞连上一根绳子；对于每个奇数$m$，他在第$m$个洞与第$3m+1$个洞之间连上一条绳子。\r\n\r\n这时B君想来剪绳子，他会剪掉那些形如（a，b）的绳子，其中a，b为绳子两边洞的编号，且满足 $a<b,a\\le n,b>n$.\r\n现给定n,你能帮B君数数他会剪掉多少根绳子吗？"},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"仅一行一个整数n."},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"仅一行一个整数表示答案。"},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"输入样例1：\r\n```\r\n12\r\n```\r\n输出样例1：\r\n```\r\n10\r\n```\r\n输入样例2：\r\n```\r\n60\r\n```\r\n输出样例2：\r\n```\r\n50\r\n```"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"$30\\%$的数据：$n \\le 100$\r\n\r\n$60\\%$的数据：$n \\le 10^6$\r\n\r\n$100\\%$的数据：$1 \\le n \\le 10^9$"}]}